TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a=random(2,5,1);
$b=random(2,7,1);
$c=$a+3;
$d=$b+2;
$a1=$a*$c;
$a2=$a*$d+$b*$c;
$a3=$b*$d;

BEGIN_TEXT


Factor the trinomial \($a1 x^2 - $a2 x +$a3\) $PAR
\[$a1 x^2 -$a2 x+ $a3=(Ax-B) (Cx-D \})\]
$BR
where \(A=\)\{ans_rule(5)\}, \(B=\)\{ans_rule(5)\}, \(C=\)\{ans_rule(5)\}, and \(D=\)\{ans_rule(5)\}, with \(A<C\) and \(B<D\).
END_TEXT


&ANS(std_num_cmp_list(.01, "", $a,$b,$c,$d));
